    <p class="w3-text-white"><span class="prompt w3-text-pink">karlwasson@home~$</span> Type <span class="syntax-highlight-command w3-text-yellow">'help'</span> to see available commands.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="terminal-input w3-padding">
    <span class="prompt w3-text-pink">karlwasson@home~$</span> <input class="w3-input w3-border-0 w3-text-white" type="text" id="terminal-input" style="display:inline;width:auto;" autofocus />
